high_descs: Turn around and go forward, go past the fridge, then turn right to face the counter with a bowl on it.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Turn left and go forward, then turn right at the fridge and go forward to the sink.
Fill the bowl with water in the sink.
Turn left and look down to face the cabinet under the counter.
Open the left cabinet, put the bowl inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with water in it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the fridge to the counter on the right.
Pick up the clear plate on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter in front of you.
Place the plate in the bottom left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the wall, then turn right and walk across the room past the refrigerator, then turn right towards the spatula on the counter.
Pick up the bowl just behind the spatula on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink, rinse it off, fill it with water, and take it out of the sink.
Turn left and walk forward to the cabinets at the corner of the counter tops.
Put the bowl in the bottom left cabinet and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl filled with water in a cabinet.
